I"ô<p>A Subsection of a level-2 will look like this</p>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-yaml" data-lang="yaml"><span class="nn">---</span>
<span class="na">sectionid</span><span class="pi">:</span> <span class="s">UNIQUE-ID</span>
<span class="na">sectionclass</span><span class="pi">:</span> <span class="s">h2</span>
<span class="na">title</span><span class="pi">:</span> <span class="s">TITLE</span>
<span class="na">parent-id</span><span class="pi">:</span> <span class="s">UNIQUE-ID-Of-PARENT</span>
<span class="nn">---</span></code></pre></figure>

<p>So the <code class="highlighter-rouge">parent-id</code> is where you will reference the anchor of the h1 section thatâ€™s your subsections parent.</p>

<p>Level 2 sections can have children, the variable to use is the same. To have children add</p>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-yaml" data-lang="yaml"><span class="na">is-parent</span><span class="pi">:</span> <span class="s">yes</span></code></pre></figure>
